name: KFC Kargo Permai
address: Jl. Cargo No.4, Ubung Kaja, Kec. Denpasar Utara, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80116, Indonesia
review 1: Drive through promo 4chickens + 2rices and free 1 pudding @77k nett, quick service, nice packaging and no queueing. Tasty fried chicken as always.
review 2: I only come for the wifi and this place has been really helpful. Much less crowded than the other one. Have a functioning ice cream machine. So far I have no problems with this since I only order beverages and stay for yhe day. Friendly staff as well as great cleanliness. I hope the bussiness runs well here since I love this place. When I can finally go back to my office, I'd spend some times here. Free parking is a plus, great as a working space!
review 3:
Brand new KFC with spacious parking area.
Clean and again, like other KFC, queuing is the hardest thing to do.
Food just like other outlet.
review 4: ...less crowded KFC outlet located in North Denpasar, also less parking lot. Drive through also available..
review 5:
Service are good they smile and greet me nicely, but the food are worth for two stars for me. They taste like had been around for 3 days or more, I am ordered package with 2 chicken and 1 rice but it taste terrible, meat are hard, and smell bad. I'm not sure if it fresh cooked or been around for more than 3 days already. It is bad experience for me.  rice are no problem just portion are very small (I'm not sure, if it same size for other kfc)sauce stand are empty, no staff upstair to maintain this. Other than this are good enough for me.

Note: I'm trying made this review as objective as much
